netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

Class DomainNameListResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainNameListResults

  • public class DomainNameListResults
extends java.lang.Object
    A results object which wraps an array of DomainNameSummaryObject items returned from a call to listDomains within the Netistrar Domain Lifecycle API. This object encodes the criteria used to obtain and sort this list as well as the total number of items for the list criteria ignoring supplied page and pageSize which allows for the development of paging GUIs.
